{"tid":2029392,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[STEAM] 影子戰場 Shadow Arena","createTime":"2020-05-22T08:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T11:28:14.000Z","uid":77769,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e24c413bc1dfc8509cb50a0d99889571f77f497c","tid":2029392,"uid":77769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T08:10:46.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GWn4FXV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGWn4FXV.png&h=e819399e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n韓國遊戲研發商珍艾碧絲（Pearl Abyss）旗下大逃殺類新作《影子戰場（Shadow Arena）》正式開放搶先體驗，玩家將可以體驗 10 位英雄特色，其中包含新登場的英雄「貝恩絲拉（Venslar）」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YD7Ah6DIhBo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYD7Ah6DIhBo&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSvRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=57fbfd3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YD7Ah6DIhBo</a><br />\n  《影子戰場》是一款由 40 名玩家一起競爭直到最後一名勝出的近戰型動作大逃殺類型遊戲，原本是《黑色沙漠》中的新遊戲模式，但官方表示因玩家迴響熱烈，決定獨立成一款遊戲並進而調整、加強。遊戲中，玩家可從不同英雄中選擇自己喜愛的冒險風格英雄進行遊戲，藉由獵殺怪物、等級提升、道具獲得來增強英雄的實力。<br />\nGameplay<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZXpflG4uXSU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZXpflG4uXSU&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSvRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=52be9bf4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZXpflG4uXSU</a>"},{"pid":"b6d60ba3d113898667830e9aa17f7a49f424b5b3","tid":2029392,"uid":21279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:03:28.000Z","msg":"睇過介紹<br />\n隻game好似好唔平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f36d06ca9cd34272e9efcd58751a970ebad7bfd1","tid":2029392,"uid":77769,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b6d60ba3d113898667830e9aa17f7a49f424b5b3","tid":2029392,"uid":21279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:03:28.000Z","msg":"睇過介紹<br />\n隻game好似好唔平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"reply